description:
Fodor's South Florida with Miami, Fort Lauderdale and the Keys(2017) - EPUB - zeke23
English | ISBN: 110188018X | 2017 | EPUB | 352 Pages | 6 MB
Written by locals, Fodor's travel guides have been offering expert advice for all tastes and budgets for more than 80 years.

With many of the state's most popular destinations, including Miami, Palm Beach, Fort Lauderdale, the Everglades, and the Florida Keys, South Florida is a vacation destination rich in possibilities for every kind of traveler. Filled with color photos, eye-popping features and fabulous maps, Fodor's South Florida is easier to browse than ever.

This travel guide includes:
Dozens of full-color maps
Hundreds of hotel and restaurant recommendations, with Fodor's Choice designating our top picks
In-depth breakout features on Art Deco Miami, Snorkeling & Scuba Diving, Everglades Ecosystems Multiple itineraries to explore the top attractions and what's off the beaten path
Coverage of Miami, Fort Lauderdale, Broward County, Palm Beach, the Treasure Coast, Key West and the Florida Keys, and the Everglades

Planning to visit more of Florida? Check out Fodor's state-wide travel guide to Florida.

Planning to focus on The Florida Keys? Check out Fodor's travel guide to The Florida Keys
